data.title: 390 Boy Cat Names for Every Letter of the Alphabet
data.meta_description: Pick the perfect name for your new furry family member with this A-to-Z list of 390 male cat names.
data.text:
Choosing a name for a male cat is fun. There are so many ways to brainstorm names that match a furry little boy kitty's cute or playful personality. Does he love to watch TV? Consider names based on Disney characters that he (or you) fixate on or names based on your boy cat's favorite sports team (or yours). Does he get riled up when you listen to country music? There are plenty of country male cat monikers to consider.

Lean into your boy cat's clownish antics by giving him a circus-inspired name. Or play up his too-cool attitude with a badass male cat name. As you get to know your boy kitty, you'll uncover his quirks, prompting you toward a unique name that fits him. Let his characteristics inspire something that describes his likes and dislikes, outlook on life, or favorite activities.

When choosing a name for your boy cat, aim for two syllables and keep it simple to pronounce. You also want to consider the names of other two-legged and four-legged (or no-legged) household members. Make your kitty's name unique so no one is confused when you call.

A couple more optionsâ€”you can also use a name generator when deciding what to call your boy cat. Then, there's always our comprehensive A-to-Z list of 390 names below, which will surely give you enough options to choose from.
